#### Limited Wish
*14th-level School of Transmutation feature*<br/>
<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

You have learned the basic principles behind the *wish* spell, allowing you to use a lessened version of it. You can spend a spell slot of 6th level or below to cast any spell one level or lower, regardless of whether it is prepared, in your spellbook, or even a wizard spell. You do not need to provide any material components for the spell, unless they cost more than <br/> 100 gp and are consumed by the spell.

You can use this ability a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus and regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.
